  <DialogueNodeData>k__BackingField:
  - guid: 5aa1c173-fef3-491c-85f9-f0f3eada6c3c
    dialogue: []
    position: {x: 100, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 1
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: be3c5da8-5ccd-460d-8d3f-016840275e45
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: ???
      <Content>k__BackingField: Hi, nice to meet you! Welcome to Ikigai Tournament!
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: ???
      <Content>k__BackingField: You must be Asuka. Word around town is that a new
        girl just got implemented into the game.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: My name's Aya! I'm here to represent the developer's
        interests and onboard newcomers.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Which basically means... I'm your boss around here.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Haha, just kidding! We're gonna be best friends!
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Unfortunately we'll still have to talk business real
        quick first.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 236, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 61cdf13b-a7c2-48e8-b6a9-647514e31de1
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Remember your job description, or do you need a refresh?
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 800, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: b07f5fa6-8227-4c1c-a2c6-a36586451d00
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In this game, pretty girls like you fight against
        big, tough robots.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Market research has proven that this is a very lucrative
        business.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: For our users, this spectacle is represented as an
        auto-battler on their phone app.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Which means that you'll do all the fighting while
        these lazy bums simply watch.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'You''ll have to put in some effort not to get crushed.
        But don''t worry! You''re not completely on your own. '
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In fact, this is our business model. The loser staring
        at you is actually our lifeline and source of income.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: During the fight, you can send out requests asking
        for healing, buffs and special attacks.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Which they have to pay for in real cash, of course.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You get it now? Your job is to...
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: SQUEEZE ALL THEIR MONEY OUT. Haha.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Fun, isn't it? It's also easier than it sounds. You
        don't have to be that good of a fighter.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Just survive and keep begging for help. They'll pay.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In fact, make sure NOT to defeat your enemies without
        sending out some requests.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Free-to-Play users just clog our servers.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1296, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: f1afe22c-d2e9-49ae-b7b1-9d6c7d70c0a9
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Time for your training day to start then! As part
        of the onboarding process, we need to test your aptitude.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You'll get two battles. Don't get defeated and make
        sure to fill up your Daily Quota.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: The fights will be against your co-worker Katoro,
        who is standing right over there.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Why don't you get acquainted before the fight?
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Katoro has been here since the release of Ikigai
        Tournament. He'll have good advice for you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Oh, and if you need to know the controls, press START
        or ESC to open the pause menu.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Come talk to me again when you're ready. I have full
        trust in you, honey!
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1900.5, y: 558.5}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  <PathToCheckpoint>k__BackingField: 
  <IsNarrativeEndReached>k__BackingField: 0
  <StartFromPreviousNarrativePath>k__BackingField: 1
